Class Summary

BlueLoanShark A type of enemy that moves faster
Character Character represents a character, hero or enemy, within the game.
GameManager This is the class that takes care of all the processes that go on in the game.
Globals Holds all the global variables used in the program
GreenLoanShark A Character enemy who gets in the hero's way.
Hero Hero is a Character and the main protagonist of the game that the user controls.

LevelManager Manages the level the player is currently on and loads the map file for them
Main Main initializes everything and starts the game.
MenuManager The manager for the main menu at the beginning of the game
MoneyBullet The MoneyBullet object being shot by the player when he has the coin-shooting power-up
OneWave This class is a thread that plays a sound once.
PhantomGain The PhantomGain enemy that appears randomly and moves through walls towards the player This Enemy represents the actual financial term of a phantom gain where investment is loss.
QuestionManager QuestionManager reads and displays finance based questions from a text file.
Thing Thing represents all the objects within the game such as characters, items, and obstacles.
Wave This class is a thread that plays a sound and loops it.
